h air supply.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Stagnant water on mushrooms will abort them.&amp;nbsp; In fact, clean water on mushrooms in a sealed terrarium will cause aborts, and that's why nobody uses them any more.&amp;nbsp; Dunking/soaking properly will not cause aborts.&amp;nbsp; Every shiitake farm in the world soaks substrates before first flush and again after each flush.&amp;nbsp; This is how it's done.&lt;br /&gt;RR</content>\n<name>RogerRabbit</name>\n<next>12082174</next>\n<prev>12081764</prev>\n<first>12076480</first>\n<last>15055197</last>\n<when>1266938175</when>\n<utime>02/23/10 05:16 PM</utime>\n</post>"}